{"tid":2431485,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"47人国安審訊，令人諗起一套2020年嘅電影","createTime":"2021-03-03T16:29:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T01:32:27.000Z","uid":80567,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b6ab18f51429655a24d237ed85b7e974890a1327","tid":2431485,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T16:29:56.000Z","msg":"The Trial of the Chicago 7<br />\n故事講述1968年反越戰情緒高漲<br />\n芝加哥發生咗動亂，即係著名嘅chicago riots<br />\n警民衝突流血（場面仲小型過呢幾年嘅示威）<br />\n然後學生領袖、組織頭目全部被捉晒去審<br />\n但遇正個黑官<br />\n針對被告、打斷講話、喺冇律師在場時審問被告<br />\n<br />\n今日47人案有部份人出嚟自辯<br />\n就更令人諗起戲中每名被告嘅自白<br />\n唔知有冇人紀錄低<br />\n但可能係佢地近期內最後一次同公眾講嘢<br />\n<br />\n喺呢十年嘅香港，法庭審訊不公大家有眼見<br />\n大興政治獄、文字獄<br />\nThe Chicago 7（一說8）呢單案得直<br />\n係多得美國健全嘅司法制度<br />\n香港嘅制度已經糜爛不堪<br />\n有冇好結果真係唔敢講<br />\n唯有了解多啲外國嘅抗爭運動<br />\n（好似美麗島事件）<br />\n保持心頭嘅溫度<br />\n<br />\n劇入面最念念不忘係呢一part：<br />\n記者問Abbie Hoffman剎停革命嘅價錢係幾多<br />\n佢答：<span class=\"red\">&rdquo;My life.&rdquo;</span><br />\n對於47人，同之前、之後<br />\n所有要審、未審、逃亡嘅人<br />\n只有致上崇高敬意<br />\n<br />\n以下係原片，演出睇netflix<br />\nSacha Baron Cohen做得好好<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/h4LJKSMVFPo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fh4LJKSMVFPo&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX8lSugA1I0CCabXjLbCjl00%3D&h=7146c5c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/h4LJKSMVFPo</a>"},{"pid":"122cda226c4899bc08ca05bef7372a5edab2d94c","tid":2431485,"uid":24044,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T16:34:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://wp.stanforddaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/chicago-poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwp.stanforddaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2Fchicago-poster.jpg&h=77d0350e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0d3982d15e2a946edd268d38225100d4f0649ec","tid":2431485,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:32:27.000Z","msg":"個狗官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]